title: Conner Brown’s Resume
text:
Business Analyst

cbrown9799@byui.edu | LinkedIn



Pursuing a Bachelor of Business Analytics at Brigham Young University - Idaho


Data Analysis, Financial Modeling, SQL & Database Management, Power BI & Data Visualization



Business Intelligence, Predictive Analytics, Financial Forecasting, Machine Learning Applications in Business




2020 - December 2024 Brigham Young University - Idaho, Rexburg, ID

Bachelor of Business Analytics
Minor in Business Finance




2023 Dean’s List, Brigham Young University - Idaho



February 2022 - Present In House Technician, Safe Streets USA (Authorized provider of ADT Security System), Rexburg, ID

Maintained good relations with customers experiencing issues with security systems.
Troubleshooted security system components like cameras, sensors, and panels.
Assisted escalated customers over the phone, providing solutions and ensuring satisfaction.

April 2021 - September 2021 Mosquito Field Service Technician, Benton County Mosquito Control District, Richland, WA

Supervised an area of land, developing skills in pesticide application and customer relations.
Monitored over 100 areas weekly, ensuring the county was free from mosquito-related dangers.

April 2020 - September 2020 Package Handler, FedEx, Pasco, WA

Managed a group of workers loading and preparing packages during the coronavirus pandemic.
Awarded Employee of the Month in July and August for teamwork, integrity, and responsibility.

October 2018 - April 2020 Full-Time Volunteer Representative, The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, Saltillo, Mexico

Served as a full-time volunteer, setting and achieving goals and providing service to others.
Developed work habits and communication skills, working in a foreign community.

August 2018 - October 2018 Potato Harvest Worker, Agri Northwest Farms, Plymouth, WA

Oversaw potato sheds and a group of workers during the harvest season.
Gained endurance, responsibility, and experience through labor-intensive work.





English (Native), Spanish (Fluent)
Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint Certification)
Ability to work in fast-paced and intense environments
